Epimorphism Installation:

1. Download & install latest cuda drivers & cuda toolkit.  Make sure LD_LIBRARY_PATH is correctly set

2. Install packages - sudo apt-get install unclutter g++ python-pyrex python-dev libportmidi-dev timidity freepats libasound2-dev mencoder

3. Install pyport midi from sources/pypm
   cd sources/pypm
   sudo python setup.py install
